description:
Two years later, a new version!

Just completely corrected drums (pretty much the entirety of the song was incorrect). Measures 36-37 on snare is soft, with accents on upbeats. Songsterr has a tendency to ignore Snare drum dynamics and play it f-fff.

Fixed the 'triplet' measures that aren't triplets (they were triplets in previous version). Didn't touch any other parts outside of those 3 measures.
title: Love Bites (So Do I)
